hildren":"What is Robots.txt?"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Robots.txt is a plain text file placed at the root of a website (for example, ",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"https://example.com/robots.txt"}],") that follows the Robots Exclusion Protocol. It contains instructions for web crawlers — primarily search engine bots — about which pages or sections they are allowed to crawl and index."]}],["$","p","8",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["When a well-behaved crawler visits a website, it first checks ",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"robots.txt"}]," before crawling any other page. If the file instructs the crawler to avoid certain pages or directories, a compliant crawler will honour those instructions."]}],["$","p","10",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Important"}],": Robots.txt is a courtesy protocol, not a security mechanism. Malicious scrapers and bots will ignore it entirely. Never use robots.txt to protect sensitive information — use server-side authentication and access controls for that."]}],["$","h2","12",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"Basic Robots.txt Syntax"}],["$","div","mid-ad-12",{"className":"my-6","children":["$","$L5",null,{"slot":"3333333333","format":"rectangle"}]}],["$","p","14",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["A robots.txt file consists of one or more records, each beginning with a ",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"User-agent"}]," directive and followed by ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Allow"}]," and/or ",["$","code","5",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Disallow"}]," directives."]}],["$","pre","23",{"className":"bg-gray-900 text-green-300 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto text-xs font-mono my-4 whitespace-pre","children":"User-agent: *\nDisallow: /admin/\nDisallow: /private/\nAllow: /public/\n\nSitemap: https://example.com/sitemap.xml"}],["$","p","25",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"User-agent"}],": Specifies which crawler the following rules apply to. The asterisk (",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"*"}],") means all crawlers. You can target specific crawlers by name (Googlebot, Bingbot, GPTBot)."]}],["$","p","27",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Disallow"}],": Specifies paths the crawler should not access. An empty Disallow value means \"allow everything.\""]}],["$","p","29",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Allow"}],": Explicitly allows a path, even within a disallowed directory."]}],["$","p","31",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Sitemap"}],": Points crawlers to your XML sitemap. Always include this."]}],["$","h2","33",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"Path Matching in Robots.txt"}],["$","p","35",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Rules apply to URL paths, not full URLs. Some matching behaviours:"]}],["$","ul","41",{"className":"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 my-3 text-gray-600 text-sm","children":[["$","li","0",{"children":["",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Disallow: /private/"}]," blocks ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/private/"}],", ",["$","code","5",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/private/page1"}],", ",["$","code","7",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/private/data/file.html"}],""]}],["$","li","1",{"children":["",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Disallow: /"}]," blocks the ",["$","strong","3",{"children":"entire site"}]," (be very careful!)"]}],["$","li","2",{"children":["",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Disallow: /*.pdf$"}]," blocks all PDF files (Googlebot supports wildcards)"]}],["$","li","3",{"children":["",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Disallow: /search?*"}]," blocks all search result pages"]}]]}],["$","h2","42",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"What to Block with Robots.txt"}],["$","p","44",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Typically block:"}],""]}],["$","ul","49",{"className":"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 my-3 text-gray-600 text-sm","children":[["$","li","0",{"children":["Admin interfaces (",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/admin/"}],", ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/wp-admin/"}],", ",["$","code","5",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/dashboard/"}],")"]}],["$","li","1",{"children":["Search result pages (",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/search?q="}],") — search-on-search creates low-quality duplicate content"]}],["$","li","2",{"children":["Cart and checkout pages (",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/cart/"}],", ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/checkout/"}],")"]}],["$","li","3",{"children":["User account areas (",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/account/"}],", ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/my-profile/"}],")"]}]]}],["$","p","50",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Do NOT block:"}],""]}],["$","ul","53",{"className":"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 my-3 text-gray-600 text-sm","children":[["$","li","0",{"children":["CSS and JavaScript files — Googlebot needs these to render your pages fully. If Googlebot cannot access CSS/JS, it cannot accurately assess your pages."]}],["$","li","1",{"children":["Any page you want indexed — this sounds obvious, but blocking a directory in robots.txt and then wondering why those pages are not indexed is a surprisingly common mistake."]}]]}],["$","h2","54",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"The Crawl Budget Concept"}],["$","p","56",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Every website has a \"crawl budget\" — the number of pages Google will crawl in a given period. For small sites, crawl budget is rarely an issue. For large sites (millions of pages), managing crawl budget matters."]}],["$","p","58",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Blocking low-value pages (parameter-based duplicates, faceted navigation combinations, utility pages) with robots.txt can help Google spend more crawl budget on your high-value pages. This is especially relevant for large e-commerce and news sites."]}],["$","h2","60",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"Robots.txt vs. Noindex — Critical Difference"}],["$","div","68",{"className":"overflow-x-auto my-5","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm border-collapse","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"className":"bg-gray-50","children":[["$","th","0",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700","children":"Robots.txt Disallow"}],["$","th","1",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700","children":"Noindex Meta Tag"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr","0",{"className":"odd:bg-white even:bg-gray-50","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Controls"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Crawling (fetching the page)"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Indexing (appearing in search results)"}]]}],["$","tr","1",{"className":"odd:bg-white even:bg-gray-50","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Googlebot accesses page?"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"No"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Yes"}]]}],["$","tr","2",{"className":"odd:bg-white even:bg-gray-50","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Page can appear in search?"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Possibly (if linked)"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"No"}]]}],["$","tr","3",{"className":"odd:bg-white even:bg-gray-50","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"Use when"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"You don't want page fetched at all"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-600","children":"You want page fetched but not shown in results"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","p","69",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Key mistake to avoid"}],": If you ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"Disallow"}]," a page in robots.txt, Google cannot crawl it to see the ",["$","code","5",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"noindex"}]," meta tag either. If you want a page excluded from search results, use the noindex meta tag — and leave the page accessible for crawling."]}],["$","h2","71",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"A Production-Ready Example"}],["$","pre","87",{"className":"bg-gray-900 text-green-300 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto text-xs font-mono my-4 whitespace-pre","children":"User-agent: *\nDisallow: /admin/\nDisallow: /wp-admin/\nDisallow: /cart/\nDisallow: /checkout/\nDisallow: /my-account/\nDisallow: /search?*\nAllow: /wp-admin/admin-ajax.php\n\nUser-agent: GPTBot\nDisallow: /\n\nSitemap: https://example.com/sitemap.xml"}],["$","p","89",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Note the GPTBot block — this AI training crawler can be blocked by many site owners who prefer their content not be used for AI training without consent."]}],["$","h2","91",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"Common Mistakes"}],["$","p","93",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Disallow: / in production"}],": Blocks your entire site from all crawlers. This is the number one robots.txt disaster — a staging site's robots.txt accidentally copied to production."]}],["$","p","95",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Blocking CSS and JS"}],": Prevents proper page rendering by Googlebot."]}],["$","p","97",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Thinking robots.txt provides security"}],": Anyone can view your robots.txt and learn exactly which paths you are trying to hide."]}],["$","p","99",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Not including a Sitemap reference"}],": Always include the Sitemap directive pointing to your XML sitemap."]}],["$","p","101",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Conflicting Allow/Disallow rules"}],": When rules conflict, most crawlers use the most specific rule. Test your rules using the robots.txt Tester in Google Search Console."]}],["$","h2","103",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","p","105",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Q: Where should I put my robots.txt file?"}],""]}],["$","p","106",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["At the root domain: ",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"https://yourdomain.com/robots.txt"}],". It must be at this exact location — subfolders like ",["$","code","3",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"/public/robots.txt"}]," will not be found. Create yours with our [Robots.txt Generator](/tools/robots-txt-generator)."]}],["$","p","108",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Q: Does robots.txt affect Google rankings?"}],""]}],["$","p","109",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Not directly. However, it controls which pages Google can crawl. Wasting crawl budget on low-value pages can indirectly reduce how often Google crawls your important pages, which can slow down the indexing of new content."]}],["$","p","111",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Q: Will blocking a page in robots.txt remove it from Google search results?"}],""]}],["$","p","112",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Not necessarily. If the blocked page has inbound links, Google may still list the URL in search results with \"No information available for this page.\" Use a ",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"noindex"}]," meta tag (on a crawlable page) to properly exclude a page from search results."]}],["$","p","114",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"children":"Q: How do I test if my robots.txt is working correctly?"}],""]}],["$","p","115",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Use the robots.txt Tester in Google Search Console, or navigate to ",["$","code","1",{"className":"bg-gray-100 text-red-600 px-1 rounded text-[0.85em] font-mono","children":"yoursite.com/robots.txt"}]," to view the file directly. Enter specific URLs to check whether they are allowed or blocked by your current rules."]}],["$","h2","117",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3","children":"Conclusion"}],["$","p","119",{"className":"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":["Robots.txt is simple but consequential. A few lines can direct search engine crawlers efficiently, preserve crawl budget, and prevent